ur nose maintain its new shape. Nasal packs or soft plastic splints also may be placed in your nostrils to stabilize the septum, the dividing wall between the air passages.&lt;/p>\n	&lt;/div>\n	&lt;/div>\n	&lt;/div>\n	</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->', 'Rhino', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '106-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-28 14:41:58', '2019-08-28 14:41:58', '', 106, 'http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/2019/08/28/106-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
