dhesives, tapes or clips close the skin incisions.&lt;/li>\n	&lt;li>&lt;i style="font-size:20px; vertical-align:middle" class="pe-7s-play margin-right-10">&lt;/i> Your tummy tuck will result in a flatter, firmer abdominal contour that is more proportionate with your body type and weight.&lt;/li>\n	&lt;/div>\n	&lt;/div>\n	&lt;/div></code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->', 'Tummy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '110-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-28 14:45:43', '2019-08-28 14:45:43', '', 110, 'http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/2019/08/28/110-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
